<p begin='00:07:01.922' end='00:07:03.757' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt; STEPHEN: I DID NOT KNOW<br/>THAT.</span></p>
<p begin='00:07:03.790' end='00:07:04.858' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>SWITCHING GEARS.</span></p>
<p begin='00:07:04.892' end='00:07:07.261' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>YOU WERE A HELICOPTER PILOT<br/>SERVING IN WHICH THEATER?</span></p>
