<p begin='00:07:07.761' end='00:07:09.062' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt; STEPHEN: OKAY.</span></p>
<p begin='00:07:09.096' end='00:07:13.934' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>AND YOUR HELICOPTER WAS SHOT<br/>DOWN, YOU LOST BOTH YOUR LEGS</span></p>
