<p begin='00:08:06.353' end='00:08:10.824' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>WOULD LIKE TO PRETEND YOU WERE,<br/>WE BOTH THINK OBAMACARE IS A</span></p>
<p begin='00:08:10.858' end='00:08:11.825' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>DISASTER.</span></p>
