<p begin='00:08:13.126' end='00:08:16.897' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt; I LIKE MY HEALTH INSURANCE I<br/>GET THROUGH THE AFFORDABLE CARE</span></p>
