<p begin='00:10:00.734' end='00:10:02.035' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt; I DISAGREE WITH YOU THERE.</span></p>
<p begin='00:10:02.069' end='00:10:03.670' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>BUT IT RHYMES.</span></p>
